translation: It's been an entire year, and I'm still dreaming of him.{#Name="Zero"}
source: It's been an entire year, and I'm still dreaming of him.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: My eye hurts like a bitch.{#Name="Zero"}
source: My eye hurts like a bitch.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: I can't believe how long it took my wounds to heal.{#Name="Zero"}
source: I can't believe how long it took my wounds to heal.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: My new arm seems good to go.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Not the most elegant of solutions, but hey,{LF}I've never been picky.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: This is a story of six sisters{#Name="Accord"}

translation: in a world protected by the power of song:{#Name="Accord"}

translation: and she won't rest until all the others are dead.{#Name="Accord"}
